#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.plot.hexbin.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.plot.hexbin"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:1
#: of
msgid "Generate a hexagonal binning plot."
msgstr "生成一个六边形箱图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:3
#: of
msgid ""
"Generate a hexagonal binning plot of `x` versus `y`. If `C` is `None` "
"(the default), this is a histogram of the number of occurrences of the "
"observations at ``(x[i], y[i])``."
msgstr ""
"生成 `x` 与 `y` 的六边形箱图。如果 `C` 为 `None`（默认值），则这是在 ``(x"
"[i], y[i])`` 位置观测值出现次数的直方图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:7
#: of
msgid ""
"If `C` is specified, specifies values at given coordinates ``(x[i], "
"y[i])``. These values are accumulated for each hexagonal bin and then "
"reduced according to `reduce_C_function`, having as default the NumPy's "
"mean function (:meth:`numpy.mean`). (If `C` is specified, it must also be"
" a 1-D sequence of the same length as `x` and `y`, or a column label.)"
msgstr ""
"如果指定了 `C`，则指定在给定坐标 ``(x[i], y[i])`` 处的值。这些值会被"
"累积到每个六边形箱中，然后根据 `reduce_C_function` 进行归约，默认使用 "
"NumPy 的均值函数 (:meth:`numpy.mean`)。（如果指定了 `C`，它也必须是与 `x`"
" 和 `y` 长度相同的 1 维序列，或一个列标签。）"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner
#: of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:14
#: of
msgid "The column label or position for x points."
msgstr "x 点的列标签或位置。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:16
#: of
msgid "The column label or position for y points."
msgstr "y 点的列标签或位置。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:18
#: of
msgid "The column label or position for the value of `(x, y)` point."
msgstr "`(x, y)` 点值的列标签或位置。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:20
#: of
msgid ""
"Function of one argument that reduces all the values in a bin to a single"
" number (e.g. `np.mean`, `np.max`, `np.sum`, `np.std`)."
msgstr ""
"将箱中的所有值归约为单个数值的函数（例如 `np.mean`、`np.max`、`np.sum`、`"
"np.std`）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:23
#: of
msgid ""
"The number of hexagons in the x-direction. The corresponding number of "
"hexagons in the y-direction is chosen in a way that the hexagons are "
"approximately regular. Alternatively, gridsize can be a tuple with two "
"elements specifying the number of hexagons in the x-direction and the "
"y-direction."
msgstr ""
"x 方向的六边形数量。y 方向的六边形数量会以使六边形近似规整的方式选择。"
"或者，gridsize 可以是一个包含两个元素的元组，分别指定 x 和 y 方向上的"
"六边形数量。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:30
#: of
msgid "Additional keyword arguments are documented in :meth:`DataFrame.plot`."
msgstr "其他关键字参数请参考 :meth:`DataFrame.plot`。"

